            "language": "en",
            "name": "Children's books in English and Arabic (online)",
            "description": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">BookSmart gives access to a free collection of books via a mobile phone.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Parents and caregivers can choose from over 75 great local and international books. These books and stories are available in English, Hindi, Spanish, and Arabic.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">The collection was carefully selected to inspire parents and caregivers to support learning after the school day or when physical schools are not in session.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">The collection includes 7 categories to read and learn from: Fun Learning Concepts, Health and Wellbeing, Nature and Science, Language Arts, Social Studies, Storybooks, and Fiction and Nonfiction.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Parents and caregivers can download their favorite books so they can keep reading without an internet connection.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">This app is optimized for all connection speeds to make sure it keeps data costs low.</span></p><p><br></p><p><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.worldreader.readtokids&amp;referrer=utm_source%3DIRC%26utm_medium%3Drefugeeinfo\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Download the Tuta Tuta app here</a>&nbsp;if you have an Android phone.</p>",
