            "description": "<p><strong>WORKEEN</strong> is an application that aims to help migrants, asylum seekers and refugees gain access to the job market. This serious game provides practical guidance and hands-on soft-skills training for anyone entering the labor market for the first time.</p><p>It is one of the first of its kind to offer interactive “training” that helps recently arrived migrant, job seekers and EU citizens that are new entrants to the labor market, effectively obtain and start a job in their new country.</p><h3>Additional Information</h3><p>The WORKEEN application is available on Google Play store for Android devices, free of charge</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
