            "description": "<p><strong>Network for Children's Rights / International Rescue Committee.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Announcement (08/10/2021</strong>) : Prosvasis will not support new registrations - <strong>Please stay tuned for Updates.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>PROSVASIS  program  aims  to  empower  unaccompanied  teens, young  refugees and migrants between 16-24 years old. The program supports participants to achieve a smooth transition to adulthood, autonomy and independence through the provision of targeted services.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Services offered:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Psychosocial and legal support</li>\n<li>Job counseling sessions and trainings</li>\n<li>Access to education</li>\n<li>Educational and non-formal training opportunities</li>\n<li>Introduction to the workplace culture in Greece</li>\n<li>Participation in advocacy and public intervention activities</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Due to COVID-19 restrictions, all services will be accessible online.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Online registration forms:</strong> Fill in the form here (<a href=\"https://forms.gle/HRC4AsUjbXiZVNWu8\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/HRC4AsUjbXiZVNWu8</a>) or send a text message via WhatsApp &amp; Viber to +306941535905.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>In case of limited internet access you could also call us every Tuesday and Thursday from 10.00 to 18.00 at 210 5148366 or daily (Monday to Friday) from 14.00 to 18.00 at 6941535905 (language of communication Greek &amp; English - for Arabic, Farsi &amp; French please send your message).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Languages spoken</strong> Greek English French Farsi/Dari Arabic.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Phone Number</strong> +306941535905</p>\n<p><strong>WhatsApp Number</strong> +306941535905</p>\n<p><strong>Viber Number</strong> +306941535905</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">This service is closed on public holidays</span> <strong>YES.</strong></p>\n<p>Is an appointment required? <strong>YES</strong> (By phone, WhatsApp, Viber, Facebook, etc.)</p>\n<p>Eligibility for services <strong>Aged 16-24 years old.</strong></p>\n",
