            "description": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45);\">INTERSOS identified the need to build up an Mental Health and Psychological Support (MHPSS)</span></p><p><br></p><p>Provision of:</p><p><br></p><ul><li>Individual case management, ensuring high-quality referrals to different social services and health care organizations on behalf of INTERSOS beneficiaries.&nbsp;</li><li>Individual psychological support in a timeframe of 3 months&nbsp;(8 to 10 sessions) completed by 5 to 6 group sessions.&nbsp;</li></ul><p><br></p><p>Languages spoken Greek English French Farsi/Dari Arabic</p><p><br></p><p>Address One Happy Family Community Center - Mytiline</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Accessibility.</strong></p><p>This service is closed on public holidays <strong>YES</strong></p><p>Eligibility for services <strong>18+, women only</strong></p><p>Are services available by referral only <strong>YES</strong></p><p>This location has female staff <strong>YES</strong></p><p>This location has separate bathrooms for men and women <strong>YES</strong></p><p>All Services Listed Are Free of Charge <strong>YES</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"color: red;\">The service can be accessed through referral from external actors. The referral pathway is currently closed</strong></p>",
