            "language": "en",
            "name": "COOKING CLASSES",
            "description": "<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">Cooking classes take place once per week.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">They are open to all beneficiaries of KYCLOS regardless of age, country of origin and gender.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">PoCs that know how to cook and they want, can enter the cooks/teachers team. </span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: windowtext;\">After every cooking class, a community kitchen takes place where food is distributed to all participants, all beneficiaries of KYCLOS that are in the premises and to the neighborhood.</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Languages spoken</strong> Greek English French Farsi/Dari Arabic Kurmanji</p>\n<p><strong>Address</strong> TOSITSA 9 ATHENS 10683</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Phone Number</strong> +30 6932927832 - FARSI, DARI, ARABIC, KURMANJI, ENGLISH, FRENCH</p>\n<p><strong>Whatsapp Number </strong>+30 6932927832 - FARSI, DARI, ARABIC, KURMANJI, ENGLISH, FRENCH</p>\n<p><strong>Viber Number </strong>+30 6932927832 - FARSI, DARI, ARABIC, KURMANJI, ENGLISH, FRENCH</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Accessibility.</strong></p>\n<p>This service is closed on public holidays <strong>YES</strong></p>\n<p>This location has female staff <strong>YES</strong></p>\n<p>All Services Listed Are Free of Charge <strong>YES </strong></p>\n",
