            "language": "en",
            "name": "TGNC (Trans and Gender Non-Conforming) Refugees in Greece: Community Building & Empowerment",
            "description": "<p>The program aims to provide social, legal and psychological support services, provision of food and non-food items, as well as community building and empowerment groups, for <strong>trans and gender non-conforming</strong> refugees, asylum seekers and migrants. The program is staffed by a social worker, a lawyer, a psychologist, a support line manager and two community building and empowerment group facilitators.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>To get in touch with the program, interested persons need to contact (<strong>via WhatsApp text message</strong>) the Emantes Support Line, +<strong>306971693446</strong>, themselves, in their chosen language, stating their basic request(s). The Support Line operates with automatic translation for languages other than Greek and English. Any further intervention (assessment, meetings with professionals) is done through interpreters, if necessary.</p>\n<p>End of program: September 2022</p>\n<p><strong>Languages spoken</strong>: Greek English French Farsi/Dari Arabic Urdu - Additional availability for Spanish. Automatic translation through the Support Line, interpreter if needed for further intervention</p>\n<p><strong>Address</strong>: Confidential</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong>Phone Number</strong> +302103802317 Greek, English</p>\n<p><strong>Whatsapp Number</strong>: +306971693446 (The Support Line operates with automatic translation for languages other than Greek and English.)</p>\n<p><strong>Emails</strong>:&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>info.emantes@gmail.com (general enquiries),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>emantes.socialservice@gmail.com (social service)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Accessibility &amp; Additional Information</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>This service is closed on public holidays YES</li>\n<li>Is an appointment required? YES (phone, WhatsApp, Viber, Facebook, etc.)</li>\n<li>Eligibility for services: Trans and Gender Non Conforming asylum seeker/refugee/migrant adults (over 18 years old)</li>\n<li>Are services available by referral only? NO - Interested persons are required to text the Emantes’ Support Line (Monday to Friday 09:00 – 17:00, +306971693446) themselves</li>\n<li>The entrance to this location has a ramp YES</li>\n<li>This location has an elevator YES</li>\n<li>This location has female staff YES</li>\n<li>This location has separate bathrooms for men and women NO</li>\n<li>All Services Listed Are Free of Charge YES</li>\n</ul>\n",
