            "description": "<p>The Regional Asylum Office of Crete became operational as an Asylum Unit of Crete on December 2016. It is based in the municipality of Heraklion on the island of Crete. It is responsible for receiving and examining applications for International Protection submitted by third-country nationals or stateless persons who are staying in the island of Crete.</p>\n<p><strong>Supervisor: Eleni Vazeou</strong></p>\n<p>Ifaistou and Elefthernis, Heraklion (Kaminia), zip code: 713 03&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3>Address in Local Language</h3>\n<p>Ελευθέρνης &amp; Ηφαιστου</p>\n",
