            "name": "Kos Passport Office",
            "description": "<p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;If your place of residence is: Kos.</strong></p><p>Applicants wishing to be issued a passport must apply, in person, at the Passport Office in their area of permanent residence. The applicant is required to fill out an&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.passport.gov.gr/en/tools/downloads/samples/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">application form</a>&nbsp;and their details are electronically registered by Passport Office personnel. The application form is printed and once the applicant proof reads and verifies the accuracy of the stated details he/she then signs the form and along with it submits the&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.passport.gov.gr/en/diadikasia-ekdosis/documents/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">necessary supporting documents</a>.</p><h3>Additional Information</h3><p>More information on Travel Documents in Greece please read this article:&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://www.refugee.info/greece/travel-documents/how-to-renew-your-travel-document\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.refugee.info/greece/travel-documents/how-to-renew-your-travel-document</a></p><p>&nbsp;<strong style=\"color: firebrick;\">Hours of operation</strong>&nbsp;<strong style=\"color: black;\">DAY OF WEEK</strong> <strong style=\"color: black;\">WORKING HOURS</strong> <strong style=\"color: black;\">APPLICATION SUBMISSION</strong> <span style=\"color: black;\">Monday - Tuesday - Thursday - Friday</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">07:30 to 15:30</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">07:30 to 15:00</span> <span style=\"color: black;\">Wednesday</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">14:00 to 22:00</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">14:00 to 21:30</span> <span style=\"color: black;\">Saturday</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">08:00 to 15:00</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">08:00 to 14:30</span>&nbsp;</p><h3>Location</h3><p>KOS</p><h3>Address</h3><p>Akti Miaouli 2</p><p>P.O.Box 85300</p><h3>Address in Local Language</h3><p>Ακτή Μιαούλη 2, T.K 85300 - ΚΩΣ</p>",
