            "description": "<p>DiH on Samos is the main NFI dsitributor for the entire Asylum seeking/ refugee population.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>DiH also provides Recreation Activites for children&nbsp;</p>\n<p>NFI Distribution&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>We provide seasonal distributions for winter and summer that targets the entire population with needed clothing, shoes and hygiene items.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>NFI referrals are provided in collaboration with all concernd actors on the island.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Monthly diaper distirbutions that target all babies and toddlers from the ages 0-4 (ages above are provided wiht diapers with a medical referral)&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong>Recreational Activites </strong></p>\n<p>Recreational activites for children target children between the ages 4-12 y/o.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Languages spoken</strong> Greek English French Arabic</p>\n<p><strong>Address  </strong>Petros Dimitriou 7 - <span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-family: DM Sans;\">831 00 Samos</span> - Vathy</p>\n<p><strong>Accessibility &amp; Additional Information</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>This service is closed on public holidays NO</li>\n<li>Is an appointment required? NO</li>\n<li>This location has female staff YES</li>\n<li>All Services Listed Are Free of Charge YES</li>\n</ul>\n",
