            "name": "Chios Regional Asylum Office",
            "description": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Open Sans;\">The Regional Asylum Office of Chios began its operations on February, 29 2016. It retains the local jurisdiction for the geographical area of Chios in the North Aegean. It operates in the Reception and Identification Center on the island of Chios. It is responsible for receiving and examining claims of International Protection submitted by third-country nationals or stateless persons who stay at the Center.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Open Sans;\"><strong>Supervisor: Kyriaki Kossena</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Open Sans;\"><strong>Address</strong></span> :&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: DM Sans;\">Offices A: LEfkonia / Kontari Chios 82100 (+30</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Open Sans;\">2271024516</span> ).</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Open Sans;\">Offices B: Reception and Identification Center Chios, Area Chalkiou Chios</span> (+30<span style=\"color: rgb(51,51,51);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: Open Sans;\">2271069021</span> ).</p>\n",
