            "language": "en",
            "name": "Baby Boxes",
            "description": "<p>Since 2018, Starfish Foundation has been providing boxes for mothers and their <strong>new-born babies.</strong></p><p><br></p><p>These boxes contain items such as sleeping bags, warm clothing for infants, underwear for the mothers, nappies, hygiene products, toys, and blankets.</p><p><br></p><p>Beneficiaries living in RIC Lesvos can pick up the Baby Boxes from the Eurorelief diapers distribution point near the main gate.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Beneficiaries living outside </strong>of RIC lesvos can come to OpenSpace community hub for request and pick up of a Baby Box.</p><p><br></p><p>Camp pick up point: Eurorelief diapers distribution point, UNHCR Tent, main gate, <strong style=\"color: red;\">Monday and Tuesday 09:00 - 13:00</strong></p><p><strong>Address</strong>:</p><p>RIC Lesvos camp Mytilene 81100 OpenSpace,</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Address</strong>: Vournazon 25, Mytilini 81132</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 80, 87);\">Starfish Foundation Community Hub, Mytilene</span></p>",
